{"id": 2469, "genre": 1001, "title": "“买买买”时代，你都还保留着哪些“我不想买”原则？", "description": "为了不掉进所谓的“当代消费主义陷阱”，你都给自己立了哪些规矩？（题图来自：iStock ©️ miakievy）", "record_count": 4485, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180727165755tazO4GSrT7lK9PW6.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-05T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 297474, "content": "不需要的东西如何实惠都不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216372}, {"id": 295174, "content": "不买超过自己消费能力的任何东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 246, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 295175, "content": "尽量避开有抄袭嫌疑的店家或者牌子", "image": null, "praise_count": 352, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 295176, "content": "看到任何“爆款”“网红款”就直接 pass", "image": null, "praise_count": 524, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 295177, "content": "如果有比较好的平价替代款，就不追求“贵妇款”", "image": null, "praise_count": 309, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 295178, "content": "不买广告打得特别洗脑/低俗/反智的品牌", "image": null, "praise_count": 745, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 297482, "content": "好看不中用的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359104}, {"id": 297994, "content": "标有清真的...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436190}, {"id": 297483, "content": "因为卖得好就理所当然认为我会买的，我偏不，我讨厌你那种理所当然的态度。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211925}, {"id": 297484, "content": "消费降维，什么都买不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297089}, {"id": 297485, "content": "不买某些明星代言的产品（比如杨颖baby）", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024275}, {"id": 297487, "content": "存钱买真正喜欢的😍", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128513}, {"id": 297999, "content": "没牌子，价格低于心里预期的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432951}, {"id": 297488, "content": "避开流量明星产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113677}, {"id": 297490, "content": "XX同款", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1420706}, {"id": 297746, "content": "超出个人购买力的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 297491, "content": "拼夕夕", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1384931}, {"id": 297492, "content": "不买弱智广告，洗脑广告的，捍卫正常的审美观！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431329}, {"id": 297493, "content": "我追的剧里穿插的广告，一定不买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425098}, {"id": 297496, "content": "买不起的就不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431362}, {"id": 297500, "content": "广告多的不买，洗脑的不买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427203}, {"id": 297504, "content": "球鞋只买实战款不买花了呼哨限定款", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431466}, {"id": 297505, "content": "怎样做一个理智的消费者？（1）量入为出，适度消费 （2）避免盲从，理性消费（3）保护环境，绿色消费 （4）勤俭节约，艰苦奋斗。来自高中一年级政治。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348325}, {"id": 297506, "content": "如无必要，勿增实体。能数字化或云方式解决的，就采用这种不占地方的方式 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429202}, {"id": 297508, "content": "对于我这种不管买啥都会犹豫而且经常犹豫到没货的人，不存在这些问题的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231731}, {"id": 297510, "content": "拼多多的不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201889}, {"id": 297511, "content": "韩版", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328801}, {"id": 297512, "content": "我需要，我喜欢，我适合", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431539}, {"id": 304680, "content": "不需要的东西再好看我也不会买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473677}, {"id": 297514, "content": "爆款敬谢不敏。另外就是各种什么砍一砍，拼多多之类的推入。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428289}, {"id": 297515, "content": "只买必需", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431559}, {"id": 297516, "content": "我不买道德败坏的明星的同款\n我不买华而不实的东西，比如说幸福感\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418192}, {"id": 297519, "content": "宣传的越好，产品往往不如宣传的那么美好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218589}, {"id": 297520, "content": "不停地心理暗示念经：上升是金牛座 上升是金牛座", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113991}, {"id": 297523, "content": "这需要分线下实体店购买和线上店铺购买吧。而且也要针对产品不同，情况不同……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344811}, {"id": 297524, "content": "能买到的纸质书绝对不买电子书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431679}, {"id": 297525, "content": "收藏品不买，一是不了解行情，再一个是还要保存，太麻烦", "image": "img/option/option/20180906001301v6XMfHJaRdZ783GS", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431674}, {"id": 298038, "content": "永无止境の需求", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391966}, {"id": 297527, "content": "不是必需品尽量不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391827}, {"id": 297528, "content": "不合身，不合意，不合理。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427008}, {"id": 297529, "content": "我不想买的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117779}, {"id": 297530, "content": "经历过两三次众筹以后，识破各种消费陷阱轻而易举！学费不高，效果明显！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 42984}, {"id": 297531, "content": "不想买只能归根于“穷”“穷”“穷”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303540}, {"id": 297532, "content": "通过贩卖焦虑或道德绑架来营销的，不买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431912}, {"id": 297535, "content": "我到底需不需要，不需要果断关掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720972}, {"id": 297536, "content": "卖卖卖 来心上", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431940}, {"id": 297537, "content": "完蛋……无保留", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227509}, {"id": 297538, "content": "无论如何，都不买实体书。再促销也不买，既不会看，又占地方，搬家太麻烦了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605858}, {"id": 297540, "content": "广告效应产品，这是最令人讨厌的，如同国产电影一样，没播之前各种噱头，上映就“4396”！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1432000}, {"id": 297541, "content": "不想买收智商税的东西，比如大部分国产保健品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116698}]}